headline: Countdown to Johnson Controls (JCI) Q1 Earnings: A Look at Estimates Beyond Revenue and EPS

headline: Johnson Controls Named to the Fortune World's Most Admired Companies 2026 List
summary: Johnson Controls (NYSE: JCI), the global leader for smart, healthy and sustainable buildings, has been named to Fortune's 2026 list of the World's Most Admired Companies.
